## Health Check
GET           /api/ping               controllers.PingController.ping
POST          /api/task               controllers.TaskController.create()
GET           /api/task/:id           controllers.TaskController.getOne(id)
GET           /api/task               controllers.TaskController.getAll()
DELETE        /api/task/:id           controllers.TaskController.delete(id)
PUT           /api/task/:id           controllers.TaskController.update(id)